===Etymology===
From {{etyl|frm|en}} {{m|frm|roan}}, probably from {{etyl|es|en}} {{m|es|roano}}, from {{etyl|osp|en}} {{m|osp|raudano}}, itself probably of {{etyl|gem|en}} origin (compare {{etyl|got|-}} {{m|got|𐍂𐌰𐌿𐌳𐌰𐌽}}, accusative of {{m|got|𐍂𐌰𐌿𐌸𐍃||red}}.

